 I do understand that it made the big group raids on the uber monsters difficult, not having all kinds of different classes but that is why there are the other blue servers. (Flame away)<br>
 But since we cannot ask the non-rp'rs to leave, and in one way it is not my right to ask them to leave, as they do pay their coin to Verant/Sony just like I do, why not take steps to make this into a very rp oriented community. <br>
 I see that there are still rp'r's out there and they so desperately want a community to call their own. Why not do it?<br>
 My 2 cent suggestion would be the following:<br>
 *2 Guilds 1 evil 1 good. The neuts can pick a side( sorry neuts)<br>
* the guilds can be in a constant state of guildwar, so this would mean no anonymous tags.RP tag fine, but no anon tag if your in either guild.<br>
*the guilds in effect would be one big Roleplayers only guild although there are 2.<br>
*the 2 guilds could set up story lines and follow them to whatever end. ie: Dark elf sk's kidnap the do gooder high elf princess. The High elves enlist the aid of the woody rangers and some dwarven warriors to bring her back, rewards and celebrations ensue, blah, blah, blah...<br>
*The roleplay could be enforced by both guilds, so no d00d's allowed.No OOC blather etc...No grief killing allowed whatsoever, no corpse camping etc, all this could be strictly eforced so there are happy campers on all sides.<br>
<br>
I understand that going PvP does not make roleplay, but I feel that it would sure add to the atmosphere.<br>
 There are so many things that I am sure that I am missing but I am only trying to help create an atmosphere that may or may not be lacking, so please keep the flames as freindly as possible.<br>
I have several friends here in tha same city that play EQ and there is a definite split between neuts, evils , and do-gooders, so we already have a start on the guilds. SO plese drop a line and offer some suggestions or veto the idea completely.<br>
<br>
my 2 cents<br>
<br>
